# 
pattern <- "[a-zA-Z0-9_]+"

word_lists <- catalog[catalog$third == "",]$name_seg
words = c()
for (i in 1:length(word_lists)){
  w_list <- word_lists[i]
  words <- c(words, w_list[[1]])
}
words <- words[!grepl(pattern, words)]
word_freqs <- arrange(freq(words), -freq)

print("")
## [1] ""
wordcloud2(data = head(word_freqs, 100))

#

#

#
